### 2. ColorSlot Enum
Define semantic color slots that all themes must implement:

```rust
/// Semantic color slots for themes
#[derive(Debug, Clone, Copy, PartialEq, Eq, Hash)]
pub enum ColorSlot {
    // Base colors
    Background,
    Foreground,

    // Semantic colors
    Primary,
    Secondary,
    Accent,

    // Status colors
    Success,
    Warning,
    Error,
    Info,

    // UI colors
    Muted,
    Border,
