| Method | Parameters | Returns | Description |
|--------|-----------|---------|-------------|
| `bold()` | none | `Style` | Make text bold |
| `italic()` | none | `Style` | Make text italic |
| `underline()` | none | `Style` | Underline text |
| `strikethrough()` | none | `Style` | Strike through text |
