#### Spacing

| Method | Parameters | Returns | Description |
|--------|-----------|---------|-------------|
| `padding(top, right, bottom, left)` | `number, number, number, number` | `Style` | Set padding in character units |
| `paddingTop(n)` | `number` | `Style` | Set top padding |
| `paddingRight(n)` | `number` | `Style` | Set right padding |
| `paddingBottom(n)` | `number` | `Style` | Set bottom padding |
| `paddingLeft(n)` | `number` | `Style` | Set left padding |
| `margin(top, right, bottom, left)` | `number, number, number, number` | `Style` | Set margin |

#### Borders

| Method | Parameters | Returns | Description |
|--------|-----------|---------|-------------|
| `border(style)` | `"normal" \| "rounded" \| "double" \| "thick"` | `Style` | Add border |
| `borderTop()` | none | `Style` | Add top border only |
| `borderRight()` | none | `Style` | Add right border only |
| `borderBottom()` | none | `Style` | Add bottom border only |
| `borderLeft()` | none | `Style` | Add left border only |

#### Dimensions

| Method | Parameters | Returns | Description |
|--------|-----------|---------|-------------|
| `width(n)` | `number` | `Style` | Set fixed width in characters |
| `height(n)` | `number` | `Style` | Set fixed height in lines |
| `maxWidth(n)` | `number` | `Style` | Set maximum width |
| `maxHeight(n)` | `number` | `Style` | Set maximum height |

